summary: Finally finished it!! I think it came out super cute c: There are a few mistakes with it, like the shapes around Meip, but that...
body:
Finally finished it!! I think it came out super cute c: There are a few mistakes with it, like the shapes around Meip, but that was an error with the pens I was using, the white gel pen I use mixes with other colours but doesnt like orange for some reason? Out of all the colours why orange…? Anyway, it was a super cute, Kawaii Desu kinda pic. I was really worried about the hair the colours with it, but I think the hair is perfect for the rest of the picture it adds a super cute Pinky Backdrop!

I mostly wanted to experiment with using other colors to shade and I’m so happy with it!! It’s hard to tell where the light source is coming from, but I didn’t really know where I wanted it to be, so that’s on me .3. Hope you all really like Meip! My super Kawaii Tumblr Aesthetic blogger OC…Who’s aesthetic changes every week
